  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the veal and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the coconut milk, tomato paste, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the curry in an earthenware bowl.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro, if desired."
